{"tid":2500971,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人行擬將螞蟻消費信貸數據交由政府控制","createTime":"2021-04-23T04:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T06:19:05.000Z","uid":361987,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d43e775dab4de15473b79b25755470fe895367fb","tid":2500971,"uid":361987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"文章日期：2021年4月23日<br />\n<br />\n英國金融時報引述消息報道，人行希望螞蟻集團將其消費信貸數據交給一家政府控制的信用評分公司，該公司將由央行前高層官員管理。不過，螞蟻集團堅持主張這一新公司應該由它領頭，但據了解人行想法的人稱，央行認為會造成利益衝突。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，該實體將服務於國有銀行與螞蟻貸款業務有競爭的其他金融機構。<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻集團拒絕置評，人行未回覆置評請求。"},{"pid":"4e84b647944cc37506d6e26f1b3a18cff661fd5b","tid":2500971,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"民企變國企, 食埋你果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539e2faa4adde848845db47da776f3cadcf35c7b","tid":2500971,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"下一步就係跟住堆data扣韭菜分<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f203b921848020c37b6e9115c4dc05c8c0f37edf","tid":2500971,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"社會主義優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等私人公司建立到成果就充公"},{"pid":"385f0ffe6a891aacd870c569cf75fc368d415564","tid":2500971,"uid":38192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"ff 一下，馬生會唔會set定個木馬潛伏係旗下所有app ？我得唔到，你都唔駛旨意有用"},{"pid":"9ebc1555d48fff45df3839c8f225f8787a4547e0","tid":2500971,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e84b647944cc37506d6e26f1b3a18cff661fd5b","tid":2500971,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"民企變國企, 食埋你果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"共產大法好<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm